OL,4,CBernie Madoff: Disgraced financier dies
OL,5,Cin prison
OL,6, Bernie Madoff, a Wall Street financier
OL,7, disgraced after he admitted to one of
OL,8, the biggest frauds in US financial
OL,9, history, has died in prison at age 82.
OL,11,FHis death was announced by the Bureau
OL,12,Fof Prisons.
OL,14,FMr Madoff had been serving a 150-year
OL,15,Fsentence after he pleaded guilty in
OL,16,F2009 to running a Ponzi scheme, which
OL,17,Fpaid investors with money from new
OL,18,Fclients rather than actual profits.
OL,20,FIt collapsed during the 2008 financial
OL,21,Fcrisis.
